This paper is likely to belong to the Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) category as it describes a new method for reducing the error in a classifier using a new type of neuron. It could also belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) categories as it involves developing a new technique for improving the performance of classifiers. Additionally, the paper mentions using the method for image classification (cs.CV) and the new neuron's ability to adjust variables on a variable by variable basis (cs.SI).
